<p>

Once your order has been logged and payment authorization has been received, we confirm receipt of the order and begin processing it. You will receive an email containing the details of your order as soon as we confirm and process it. In this mail you will be provided with a unique Order ID (eg. AB0123456), a listing of the item(s) you have ordered and the expected delivery time. You will also be notified when we ships the item(s) to you.  You can track your order status in your 'My Account' dashboard.
